.TH AUTOpot 1 "19 April 2011" "1.0" "AUTOPot.pl"
.SH NAME
AUTOpot.pl \- Generates a mathlink executable from a POTLib fortran library
.SH SYNOPSIS
perl AUTOpot.pl [OPTION] LIBFILE NAME LIB
.SH DESCRIPTION
The AUTOpot script generates a MathLink executable from LIBFILE (that uses the LIB library) to a folder NAME or takes a list from a CSV file.
.SH OPTIONS
.IP "-m"
Automaticlly runs 
.B make
for each library generated
.IP "-c CSV count"
Pulls the LIBFILE NAME and LIB from a comma seperated values list instead of arguments. Make sure your count is correct and the headers are
.B LIBFILE, NAME, & LIB
It is CASE SENSITIVE!
.SH AUTHOR
Aaron Tagliaboschi (aaron.tagliaboschi@gmail.com)
